		</dt>
		<dd class="comment ">
		<div class="format_text">
		<p>I had some trouble with the 2lbs of sausage on a 5&#215;5 square. Seems to be too much on a small space and I couldn&#8217;t get it rolled up. I made 2 versions that works equally well. First was the 5&#215;5 but I only used .5lbs of sausage. Worked great. Second version was 2lbs bacon, 2 lbs sausage on a 10&#215;10 square. Worked good too. Not quite as bacon-y as the smaller version, but still good. Also, on the second version I added 1lb of shredded sharp cheddar cheese. Excellent improvement!</p>
<p>Great recipe!!!!!</p>
		</div><!-- format text -->

		</dd>



	
