		<div class="format_text">
		<p>This was a great reason to buy a smoker. We had to get an indoor smoker to and the recipe works great but did not take 2.5 hours. Is that a typo? Seems like a long time unless indoor smokers do it quicker at the same temps&#8230; </p>
<p>But had to test it out on some chicken and veggies and found a new love: the indoor smoker. Only 28 minutes for three huge marinated chicken breasts. I know it may be sacrilege for hardcore BBQ&#8217;ers but it&#8217;s winter, we have no backyard, and for $40 it replaced the George Foreman. Buh-bye.</p>
		</div><!-- format text -->

		</dd>



	
