			<dt class="comment ">
		<span class="comment_author"><a href='http://www.burntfingerbbq.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Jason</a></span>
		<span class="comment_time">April 30, 2009</span>
		</dt>
		<dd class="comment ">
		<div class="format_text">
		<p>@Dave &#8211; Try finding a gourmet meat shop in your town.  Chances are they carry some fantastic artisan sausage.  In regards to cheese, just be prepared for it leak out.  If you&#8217;re having trouble keep the rolling together, try to rolling as tight as possible and squeeze out all the air bubbles.  A thinner layer of sausage that&#8217;s rolled over a couple times works better than a thick that&#8217;s only rolled once.  Enjoy!</p>
		</div><!-- format text -->

		</dd>



	
