		<p>Bob,  Cheese is tricky when slow cooking.  Try some high melt cheese.  Hi Mountain has some good blends.  Grated cheese will disappear.  I&#8217;ve tried the cheese thing on a few of these bad boys with grated and other cheeses, but they never survive on my Traeger.  The high melt cheese is key.  Any other thoughts from fatty or PETA need not apply.  BE peeps, let me know what you think.</p>
