		<div class="format_text">
		<p>Bacon Explosion is actually a new version of Morcon. It is still rolled with foil paper and baked in the oven. The difference between Morcon and Bacon Explosion is that, Bacon Explosion is easy to be mise-en-place and it is easy to be cook because of the thin meat of bacon and Morcon is the opposite. The doneness of the meat which is the bacon is medium well to attain its juiciness of the meat and probably with an apple sauce or honey; this Bacon Explosion experience would be appetizing.</p>
