			<dt class="comment ">
		<span class="comment_author">Ed</span>
		<span class="comment_time">August 22, 2010</span>
		</dt>
		<dd class="comment ">
		<div class="format_text">
		<p>I make one of these every few months&#8230; One on the smoker right now actually&#8230; I have broiled one when in an apartment when my smoker was in storage&#8230; I have used spicy sausage&#8230; Tried different bacons, different sauces&#8230; And no matter what&#8230; It still tastes amazing&#8230; My friends are always surprised how not greasy it is&#8230; The fat just melts off and leaves it juicy.</p>
		</div><!-- format text -->

		</dd>



	
