			<dt class="comment ">
		<span class="comment_author"><a href='http://www.burntfingerbbq.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>Jason</a></span>
		<span class="comment_time">March 20, 2011</span>
		</dt>
		<dd class="comment ">
		<div class="format_text">
		<p>@Vicky &#8211; Yes, we grind our own sausage.  We prefer to leave the bacon out of the grind so that the pieces are bigger, and to help keep them from getting soggy.  We like our Explosions with a crispy bacon center, so we hold off on adding the fried bacon until the very last second!</p>
		</div><!-- format text -->

